Class Operation

  • java.lang.Object
    • Operation

  • public class Operation
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    pratikkarnik and scottfloam

    Operation

    The Operation class stores information about each action performed in the system. For example, the Operation, R(T1,x1), indicates that Transaction 1 would like to read Variable x1.
